.TH "LIGHTNING-NODE-LISTFORWARDS-IN-MSAT-SKEWNESS" 1 "May 2026" "lightning 0.6.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
lightning-node-listforwards-in-msat-skewness \- FEAT-2821 node-listforwards-in-msat-skewness
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B lightning node-listforwards-in-msat-skewness
.SH DESCRIPTION
Computes skewness of incoming msat values across settled forwards for the local node (FEAT-2821).
.PP
Output: JSON from CLN.
.TP
.B in_msat_skewness
Fisher-Pearson skewness of in_msat values from settled forwards.
.TP
.B n
Number of data points used.
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
Always.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR lightning(1)
